      <title>I had the privilege of collaborating with @themuseumofmodernart , bringing to li...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DJwyFVgMNo9/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/499424976_18480209335070968_5667483920358870205_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzYzNDYxOTQ1NDg2MDc4NTgwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5MDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=6Duu3YwpoCMQ7kNvwE4yaNM&amp;_nc_oc=AdpgAppi2yBO1z6MhTcqeAgnggBnxNPQAX1kBrIuzNx1uXxMJ_zfTfza7b0mIAA0klk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=LtAYzzr9xwMn1_pq9W9U5Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwmyrggMiY9wniOxn7dv2MpHucigcn1z9_Liozv1B6qhA&amp;oe=69C8E8C0" alt="Instagram billede fra @gaiaesthermaria" /></p><p><strong>@gaiaesthermaria</strong></p><p>I had the privilege of collaborating with @themuseumofmodernart , bringing to life a somatic exercise, recited by somatic therapist Emily Price on how to process overwhelming feelings raised by looking at art. I wanted to represent an everchanging shapeshifting inscape, that could mimick the kynetic of our own feelings - often slippery and difficult to get a hold of. With something like 2000 straight ahead drawings 😵‍💫.<br/>
Find a snippet here, some more soon. Perhaps you can also take the exercise? ☺️<br/>
#artist #drawing #animation #somaticexercise #traditionalanimation #handdrawn #handdrawnanimation #2danimation #moma #framebyframe #framebyframeanimation #morphing #surreal #paper #charcoal #oilpastels #coloredpencils #paper <br/>
Many thanks to DaeQuan Alexander Collier and Arlette Hernandez @wokegrandma for their trust and work ♥️</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/499424976_18480209335070968_5667483920358870205_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzYzNDYxOTQ1NDg2MDc4NTgwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5MDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=6Duu3YwpoCMQ7kNvwE4yaNM&amp;_nc_oc=AdpgAppi2yBO1z6MhTcqeAgnggBnxNPQAX1kBrIuzNx1uXxMJ_zfTfza7b0mIAA0klk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=LtAYzzr9xwMn1_pq9W9U5Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwmyrggMiY9wniOxn7dv2MpHucigcn1z9_Liozv1B6qhA&amp;oe=69C8E8C0" alt="Instagram billede fra @gaiaesthermaria" /></p><p><strong>@gaiaesthermaria</strong></p><p>I had the privilege of collaborating with @themuseumofmodernart , bringing to life a somatic exercise, recited by somatic therapist Emily Price on how to process overwhelming feelings raised by looking at art. I wanted to represent an everchanging shapeshifting inscape, that could mimick the kynetic of our own feelings - often slippery and difficult to get a hold of. With something like 2000 straight ahead drawings 😵‍💫.<br/>
Find a snippet here, some more soon. Perhaps you can also take the exercise? ☺️<br/>
#artist #drawing #animation #somaticexercise #traditionalanimation #handdrawn #handdrawnanimation #2danimation #moma #framebyframe #framebyframeanimation #morphing #surreal #paper #charcoal #oilpastels #coloredpencils #paper <br/>
Many thanks to DaeQuan Alexander Collier and Arlette Hernandez @wokegrandma for their trust and work ♥️</p>]]></content:encoded>
